snippet.title: AwakenTheWorldFilm
snippet.description:
Films for the awakening of human consciousness. Please subscribe to the mailing list at http://www.awakentheworld.com.
The AwakenTheWorldFilm channel and the Awaken the World initiative are run by Daniel Schmidt and Tanya Mahar.
Follow us on Facebook at: www.facebook.com/awakentheworldfilm
